<!-- 
    GetParameterValues Notes:
    1. Can request specific parameters or use partial paths ending with '.'
    2. Partial paths return all sub-parameters
    3. ParameterNames array can contain mix of full and partial paths
    4. Response contains exact parameter names and typed values
    5. Unknown parameters result in fault 9005 (Invalid parameter name)
-->